title: #540 - Joey Diaz and Lee Syatt
description:
Joey Diaz tells Lee Syatt what his three days on tour with Wheeler Walker Jr were like and why he likes those kinds of shows. Joey also tells Lee about his very first days in comedy, and how fear can hold us back.
